  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Guard

    public class JobPlannerAllAccessPermission
extends ClientPermission
    If pa.scheduler.core.tenant.filter is enabled, this permission allows a user to fully control the job planner, regardless of which tenant the user belongs to.
